</style>（即样本平均值）具有近似正态分布，平均值为<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mu"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">μ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，方差<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\frac {{\sigma}^2} {n}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mfrac"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 0.906em; padding: 0px 0.12em;">为<span class="mjx-numerator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 1.281em; top: -1.631em;"><span class="mjx-msubsup" style=""><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.001em;"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.001em;">σ</span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 83.3%; vertical-align: 0.435em; padding-left: 0.062em; padding-right: 0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 1.281em; bottom: -0.524em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 0.906em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 1.524em; vertical-align: -0.37em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，其中<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\sigma ^ 2"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.001em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.001em;">σ</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0.073em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>是基础分布的方差。这意味着标准差为<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\frac {\sigma} {\sqrt n}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mfrac"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 1.155em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 1.633em; top: -1.148em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.001em;">σ</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 1.633em; bottom: -1.059em;"><span class="mjx-msqrt" style=""><span class="mjx-box" style="padding-top: 0.045em;"><span class="mjx-surd"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">√</span></span> <span class="mjx-box" style="padding-top: 0.236em; border-top: 1px solid;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 1.155em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 1.561em; vertical-align: -0.749em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。注意那里的平方根——这很重要。样本均值的标准差与样本量的平方根成正比。这意味着回报迅速递减，这是非线性的。这里的寓意是越大越好，但也不是那么好 - 从 10 ->; 100 个项目的样本量中获得的效果比从 100 ->; 1000 个项目中获得的效果要多得多。将标准差减少<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="n"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>需要<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="n^2"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span>另外<span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2 个</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>数据点。</p><h1>交际理论法的实践</h1><p>这如何适用于一开始的示例？让我们尝试一下：</p><h2>铸币</h2><p>在这种情况下，基础随机变量（硬币的重量）可以建模为均值为 25g、方差为 1 的正态分布（这给出了 ±0.5g 的方差 - 使其更像是一个硬分布）。限制，必须使用 0.05 之类的方差）。</p><p>对 100 个项目的批次运行 1000 次模拟得出的标准差为 0.07。这是有道理的，因为<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\frac {\sqrt {0.5 }} {\sqrt {100 }} = 0.07"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mfrac"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 1.791em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 2.533em; top: -1.766em;"><span class="mjx-msqrt" style=""><span class="mjx-box" style="padding-top: 0.045em;"><span class="mjx-surd"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">√</span></span> <span class="mjx-box" style="padding-top: 0.119em; border-top: 1px solid;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.5</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 2.533em; bottom: -1.059em;"><span class="mjx-msqrt" style=""><span class="mjx-box" style="padding-top: 0.045em;"><span class="mjx-surd"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">√</span></span> <span class="mjx-box" style="padding-top: 0.119em; border-top: 1px solid;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">100</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 1.791em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 1.998em; vertical-align: -0.749em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.07</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。这反映在图表中，平均重量在 24.8 - 25.25 克之间。使用大 10 倍的批次只会使标准开发变小约 2 倍，这很好，但会涉及更多的工作。</p><p>这应该完全足以抓住你不成熟的骗子！至少制造每枚硬币重24.7克的类型，希望您不会注意到。如果他们每 10 枚硬币就削掉一点，或者制作平均 24.5 克的硬币，但时不时地扔进更重的硬币，这也行吗？我还没有深入探讨这一点，但它似乎也会起作用 - 因为结果分布也会有平均值和标准差，在大多数情况下与预期的不同。 </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/dgwuygdk8fkguobflhnx" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/waan74azdi3intviffam 153w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/ncmswszw1opa6oxgahdv 233w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/diawsbkwurpb9kjmsmvw 313w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/vntj5xivzy76j6rkif4n 393w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/bxmtn9v22omyafiycfqb 473w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/k7nsrkkstri20jznaogw 553w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/fytxshzct8ygpryqevdt 633w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/t4w0sqe9ivfkhrmdkbvp 713w"></figure><h2>网络错误</h2><p>网络错误（假设它们是独立的 - 嘿！）可以建模为二项式分布，即<code>n</code>次试验，每次试验都有成功的概率<code>p</code> 。在本例中，每秒请求数为 10k，错误率为 0.2%，即<code>Binomial(1000, 0.002)</code> 。假设每分钟收集一次指标，这为我们提供了<code>60s * 1k requests</code>批次，即每批次<code>60 000</code>次试验。每小时有 60 分钟，因此总共应该有约<code>3 600 000</code>请求。其中 0.2% 应该是错误，因此我们预计会收到 7200 个错误，或 3,592,800 个成功请求。在示例中，有 6800 个错误。这可以吗？</p><p>根据计算，运行 1000 次模拟平均获得约 3,592,775 次成功，这几乎是理想的（毕竟 60k 是一个巨大的样本）。话虽这么说，在 1000 次试验中，几乎从未产生过 6840 个错误 - 总是有更多错误。因此，尽管 0.2% 看起来差不多是 0.19%，但当样本量如此大时，就会产生很大的差异。这在理论上也成立吗？样本平均值误差计数的实验标准偏差为 86.7。这意味着大约 68% 的每分钟错误计数应为 7200 ± 87。大约 96% 的每分钟错误计数应为 7200 ± 174。这是一个非常窄的范围。这就是您从如此大的样本量中得到的结果。这也检查是否进行了显式计算。二项式分布的方差为<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\sigma ^2 = k \dot p \dot (1 - p)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.001em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.001em;">σ</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0.073em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">k</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-munderover"><span class="mjx-stack"><span class="mjx-over" style="height: 0.17em; padding-bottom: 0.06em; padding-left: 0.085em;"><span class="mjx-mo" style="vertical-align: top;"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">˙</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-op"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-munderover"><span class="mjx-stack"><span class="mjx-over" style="height: 0.17em; padding-bottom: 0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mo" style="vertical-align: top;"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">˙</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-op" style="padding-left: 0.055em;"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">−</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，其中<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="k"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">k</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>是试验次数， <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="p"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>是成功概率。因此，在本例中<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\sigma ^2 = 60,000 \cdot (1 - 0.002) \cdot 0.002 = 119.76"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.001em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.001em;">σ</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0.073em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">60</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">000</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.004em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">⋅</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">−</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.002</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.004em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">⋅</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.002</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">119.76</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>且<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\sigma = 10.94"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.001em;">σ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">10.94</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。 60 个批次的标准差应为<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\frac {10.94} {\sqrt 60} = 1.41"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mfrac"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 1.752em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 2.478em; top: -1.405em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">10.94</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 2.478em; bottom: -1.059em;"><span class="mjx-mrow" style=""><span class="mjx-msqrt"><span class="mjx-box" style="padding-top: 0.045em;"><span class="mjx-surd"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">√</span></span> <span class="mjx-box" style="padding-top: 0.119em; border-top: 1px solid;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">6</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0</span></span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 1.752em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 1.743em; vertical-align: -0.749em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1.41</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。将其乘以 60（批次数）会将其从平均值的 std dev 转换为计数的 std dev，检查结果为<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="1.41 \cdot 60 = 84.77"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1.41</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.004em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">⋅</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">60</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">84.77</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，这与经验结果足够接近。</p><p>该示例中有 6840 个错误，比预期少 360 个，与 0.2% 错误率平均值相差 4.4 个标准差。这意味着有些可疑的事情正在发生，但是以积极的方式发生的？因为错误比预期少？有趣……不过，可能要等到明天。这可以… </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/h0vubaisrdbgc1uqnbih" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/uio9og8btot2uzz9kuda 159w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/uelxe1gjmwlvosuavfah 239w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/c9jw1zy6o1qco1bw9llh 319w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/jzkyiko7khuofthxmzed 399w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/dozcfwboajgpw9r1ot4a 479w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/g5lkkecvyptjqhpph6rx 559w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/mtoejqxeiufrraqimjn2 639w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/gfnnhm5idccwyherwbdc 719w"></figure><h2>派对</h2><p>该分布将假设（离散）均匀分布，即 90-110 之间的任何值都是同等可能的。泊松或二项式在这里可能更现实，但这并不重要。在本例中，批量大小为 52，因为我们的想法是每周召开一次会议。</p><p> 1000 次模拟的结果是平均值为 100（如果不是的话那就奇怪了……），标准差为 0.84。这在理论上有意义吗？均匀分布的方差为<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span c