span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 5.728em; bottom: -0.665em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">12</span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 4.051em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 1.793em; vertical-align: -0.47em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，其中<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="a, b"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">a</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">、</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">b</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>是最小值和最大值。所以在这种情况下， <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\sigma ^2 = \frac {(110 - 90 + 1)^2 - 1} {12} = 36.(6)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.001em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.001em;">σ</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0.073em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 5.141em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 7.27em; top: -1.87em;"><span class="mjx-mrow" style=""><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">110</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">−</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">90</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">+</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 83.3%; vertical-align: 0.435em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">−</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 7.27em; bottom: -0.665em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">12</span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 5.141em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 1.793em; vertical-align: -0.47em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">36。</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">6</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。 52 次会议的预期标准差应为</p><p><span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\frac \sigma {\sqrt 52} = 0.84"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mfrac"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 1.438em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 2.033em; top: -1.148em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.001em;">σ</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 2.033em; bottom: -1.059em;"><span class="mjx-mrow" style=""><span class="mjx-msqrt"><span class="mjx-box" style="padding-top: 0.045em;"><span class="mjx-surd"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">√</span></span> <span class="mjx-box" style="padding-top: 0.119em; border-top: 1px solid;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">5</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 1.438em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 1.561em; vertical-align: -0.749em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.84</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。这与生成的模拟完全相同。</p><p>由于 3 个标准差包含 99.73% 的值（通过<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/68%E2%80%9395%E2%80%9399.7_rule">68-96-99.7</a>规则），因此似乎为<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="52 \cdot (100 ± 3)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">52</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.004em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">⋅</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">100</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">±</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">3</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>人提供足够的东西，即足够 5044 到 5356 人使用应该完全没问题。这比仅仅为<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="52 \cdot (100 ± 10)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">52</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.004em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">⋅</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">100</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">±</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">10</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>人提供足够的数量要好得多，因为这将是 4680 到 5720 之间的范围，或者 1040 与 312 之间的差异 - 这是一个大 3 倍的跨度！为 5300 人提供足够的数量似乎已经足够了。 </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/wjq8dhuscpr6yvm8zbzf" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/mag5bb5mqdetopnmtckk 148w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/y1xnrguinbzug1a8sxrr 228w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/f4ju9oul6bwi6nueyddw 308w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/cvhcna6ukus5jzvj5mrl 388w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/kojeva9akrjnanpoyxc1 468w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/tpxue4jh2mq84dqfumlv 548w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/rj3zlskido8bcpmvz1jh 628w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/wbbkvdkcf9j2p0mdjt6w 708w"></figure><h2>观鸟</h2><p>这里假设<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda = 3"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，即每个地方或多或少发现了 3 只啄木鸟。为了使这个更加现实，我们假设您有 10 次之前行程的计数，即<code>[4, 5, 1, 6, 3, 4, 2, 1, 1, 0]</code> 。您要求 ChatGPT 为您估计<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>参数，就像人们所做的那样，它会回答：</p><blockquote><p>泊松分布的 lambda 参数通常被估计为数据的平均值。要计算提供的数据<code>[4, 5, 1, 6, 3, 4, 2, 1, 1, 0]</code> ，您可以将所有数字加在一起，然后除以数字的计数。</p><p>值之和： <code>4 + 5 + 1 + 6 + 3 + 4 + 2 + 1 + 1 + 0 = 27</code>计数： <code>10</code>值平均值： <code>27 / 10 = 2.7</code></p><p>因此，该数据的估计 lambda 参数为<code>2.7</code> 。</p></blockquote><p>到目前为止，一切都很好。但10张支票似乎并不算多。您应该数数多少次才能确定这一点？ 10 次计数的标准差为 0.54。需要多少才能使 3 个标准偏差达到 1 左右（因为这意味着 99% 的情况下您都会得到正确的 lambda）？</p><p>泊松分布的方差就是它的<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>参数，该参数可能约为 3。如果样本量足够大，样本均值将与<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的实际值相差 ± 0.5 99%时间（假设所有林地都是相同的，包括天气、一天中的时间等 - 这不是很有趣吗！）。所以你想要的是找到<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="n"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>使得<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\sigma = \frac {\sqrt \lambda} {\sqrt n}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.001em;">σ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 1.155em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 1.633em; top: -1.766em;"><span class="mjx-msqrt" style=""><span class="mjx-box" style="padding-top: 0.045em;"><span class="mjx-surd"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">√</span></span> <span class="mjx-box" style="padding-top: 0.11em; border-top: 1px solid;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 1.633em; bottom: -1.059em;"><span class="mjx-msqrt" style=""><span class="mjx-box" style="padding-top: 0.045em;"><span class="mjx-surd"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">√</span></span> <span class="mjx-box" style="padding-top: 0.236em; border-top: 1px solid;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 1.155em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 1.998em; vertical-align: -0.749em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，其中<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\sigma = \frac 1 3"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.001em;">σ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 0.495em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 0.7em; top: -1.372em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 0.7em; bottom: -0.686em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">3</span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 0.495em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 1.456em; vertical-align: -0.485em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> （因为 99% 是 3 个标准偏差）并且<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda = 3"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> （泊松分布的方差是<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，因此这里必须对其进行平方根）。经过几次转换后，您有<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="n = \frac {(\sqrt \lambda) ^2} {\sigma ^ 2} = \frac \lambda {\sigma ^ 2} = 3 \cdot \frac 1 { ({\frac 1 3}) ^2} = 27"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 2.017em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 2.852em; top: -1.88em;"><span class="mjx-mrow" style=""><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-msqrt"><span class="mjx-box" style="padding-top: 0.045em;"><span class="mjx-surd"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">√</span></span> <span class="mjx-box" style="padding-top: 0.11em; border-top: 1px solid;"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 83.3%; vertical-align: 0.435em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 2.852em; bottom: -0.85em;"><span class="mjx-msubsup" style=""><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.001em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.001em;">σ</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 83.3%; vertical-align: 0.347em; padding-left: 0.062em; padding-right: 0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 2.017em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 1.93em; vertical-align: -0.601em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 0.906em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 1.281em; top: -1.412em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 1.281em; bottom: -0.85em;"><span class="mjx-msubsup" style=""><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.001em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.001em;">σ</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 83.3%; vertical-align: 0.347em; padding-left: 0.062em; padding-right: 0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 0.906em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 1.6em; vertical-align: -0.601em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">3</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.004em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">×</span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 1.598em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 2.26em; top: -1.372em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 2.26em; bottom: -1.614em;"><span class="mjx-mrow" style=""><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mfrac"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 0.583em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="font-size: 83.3%; width: 0.7em; top: -1.288em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="font-size: 83.3%; width: 0.7em; bottom: -0.709em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">3</span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 0.583em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 1.664em; vertical-align: -0.591em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 83.3%; vertical-align: 0.347em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.06em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.296em; width: 1.598em;" class="mjx-line"></span></span><span style="height: 2.111em; vertical-align: -1.141em;" class="mjx-vsize"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">27</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。</p><p>这检查出来了吗？对<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda = 3"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的泊松分布中的 27 个项目进行 1000 次模拟，结果标准偏差为 0.33。这正是我们想要的！所以你现在可以去检查另外 17 个补丁来获取丢失的数据，然后最终发布另一篇论文！一旦你弄清楚如何为此计算 p 值...... </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/cxa6zo7rka0nd0a8xbmq" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/qgnia3eedvjcgqg5x3c1 83w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/ybumeibpkry3ld9rn5gf 163w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/bgwlubag1bsfrfukosuz 243w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/efxc6g4zpwoo6coikuyp 323w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/mdu9greyo93p8f3i8cvh 403w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/jtaemendwssvyxhnnwai 483w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/gltgkijtlzconpsqlyky 563w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/t7eq2vfxvruowlulj7bt 643w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr